---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sports Digital Network - Where Community Comes Together"
  description="Canada's premium digital out-of-home advertising network. Connect your brand with 3.6M weekly visitors at community arenas, recreation facilities, and golf courses."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div>
        <h1>Where Community <span class="highlight">Comes Together</span></h1>
        <p>In the arenas where families meet after work, on the greens where deals are made, and in the spaces where kids chase dreams—your brand becomes part of the moments that matter.</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="/advertisers" class="btn btn-primary">For Advertisers</a>
          <a href="/venues" class="btn btn-secondary">Partner With Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-number">3.6M</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Weekly Visits</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Premium Venues</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-number">35M</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Impressions/Week</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-number">350</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Ad Plays/Day</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="insight">
    <div class="insight-container">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Local Media Gap</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">As local newspapers closed, radio stations consolidated, and storefront windows went dark, something remarkable happened.</p>
      <div class="insight-box">
        <strong>Community gathering places didn't disappear—they got busier.</strong><br><br>
        The arenas, golf courses, and rec centers where people show up for each other week after week became the last true local hubs. And that's where your message belongs.
      </div>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">&#127919;</div>
          <h3>Captive Attention</h3>
          <p>Your audience isn't scrolling. They're present, engaged, and spending quality time in our venues—an average of 90 minutes per visit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">&#127969;</div>
          <h3>True Local Reach</h3>
          <p>Connect with families, decision-makers, and community leaders right where they gather—no wasted impressions on people outside your market.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">&#9889;</div>
          <h3>Premium Context</h3>
          <p>Your brand appears in venues that communities are proud of—spaces associated with achievement, family time, and positive moments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="venues">
    <div class="venues-container">
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">Our Network</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="text-align: center;">Premium facilities across Canada's most vibrant communities</p>
      <div class="venues-grid">
        <div class="venue-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515703407324-5f753afd8be8?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Hockey arena with spectators">
          <div class="venue-overlay">
            <h3>Multi-Pad Arenas</h3>
            <p>Where families gather and communities connect every week</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="venue-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587174486073-ae5e5cff23aa?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Premium golf course">
          <div class="venue-overlay">
            <h3>Premium Golf Courses</h3>
            <p>Exclusive access to affluent, decision-making demographics</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to Be Where Community Happens?</h2>
    <p>Let's talk about bringing your brand into the spaces that matter most to your customers.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-white">Get Started Today</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
